                    <h1 class="title citation_title" itemprop="name">Scientific Elegance in NIDS: Unveiling Cardinality Reduction, Box-Cox Transformation, and ADASYN for Enhanced Intrusion Detection</h1>
                                   
                    <p class="authors citation_author">
                        Amerah Alabrah<sup>*</sup>                    </p>

                    <p class="affiliation">
                        
Department of Information Systems College of Computer and Information Sciences, King Saud University, Riyadh, 11451, Saudi Arabia                    </p>

                                            <p class="Corresponding">

                        * Corresponding Author: Amerah Alabrah. Email: <img style="vertical-align: middle" alt="email" src="https://www.techscience.com/psh.php?mailname=aalobrah@ksu.edu.sa" />  

                        </p>
                    
                                        <p class="cite-info">
                       <i>Computers, Materials &amp; Continua</i> <b>2024</b>, <i>79</i>(3), 3897-3912. <a href="https://doi.org/10.32604/cmc.2024.048528">https://doi.org/10.32604/cmc.2024.048528</a>                    </p>
                    <p class="article-date">
                         <strong>Received</strong> 11 December 2023; <strong>Accepted</strong> 14 February 2024;                         <strong>Issue published</strong> 20 June 2024                        
                                            </p>
                                        
                                        
                                        
                                        
                </div>
